text: Naagin 2 is an Indian television series. The series was the sequel of Naagin and is followed by Naagin 3, The series is produced by Ekta Kapoor, and created by Balaji Telefilms. The series premiered on Colors TV on 8 October 2016 and ended on 25 June 2017. The series starred Mouni Roy and Karanvir Bohra in lead roles. ==References== Category:2016 Indian television series debuts
title: Naagin 2
